data.description: Run, don't walk! Here's the one-level, split bedroom, all brick home on an oversized lot in Effingham County you've been waiting for. Home boasts custom wood cabinetry, granite countertops, LVP flooring, and front and back yard irrigation. The cul-de-sac drive and nearly 3/4-acre lot allows you to enjoy the quiet life while still being within 25 mins to SAV/HH Int Airport, Gulfstream, and major shopping and restaurants. Move in ready with high ceilings, tons of natural light, and tasteful, neutral finishes. Work from home or host guests often? No problem. The floorplan and bedroom count can easily accommodate your current stage of life.
